<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Noon-tide" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Noon-tide,</orth> midday: <cit><quote>displease her brother's n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 55</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>makes the n. night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.77" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 77</bibl></cit>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>his weary n. prick,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 781" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 781</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the n. sun,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>at the n. prick,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 34</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>